snippet.textDisplay: AWESOME. WOW. Where to start? Musical fusion and composition stirring as always. This time around visual presentations has outdone all. Keeping S.M. Sultan's painting in the background, Sultan's inspiration is apparent in costumes, sound stage design, and even the screens that are used to decorate the guitars. S.M.Sultan has always seen Bengal as a land of strong and colorful people. The overall ambiance of the song is of a village adjacent to a forest, and all the nuanced references to Bengali folklore have changed the game.
